snippet.textDisplay: of course its a new try to uplift Odia but some things has its own identity and respect. in any song not only the music is important but also the wordings are also important because it carries the true meaning and the original thoughts the poet wants to present. we should not tamper with these; without originality nothing lasts for long. The step is good but approach is not good. Please don't try it further. RANGABATI IS NOT ONLY A SAMBALPURI FOLK SONG BUT ALSO AN IDENTITY OF SAMBALPUR(WESTERN ODISHA). IT'S REALLY PAINING.
